@startuml
title Sequence diagram (Processo di login) - Iterazione 2

actor User as U
participant "Frontend"          as FE
participant "API Gateway"       as GW
participant "Auth Controller"   as AC
participant "Auth Service"      as AS
participant "Profile Repository" as PR
participant "MongoDB"           as DB

U  -> FE  : Inserisce credenziali
FE -> GW  : POST /login
GW -> AC  : Login
AC -> AS  : Autenticazione
AS -> PR  : Cerca utente per matricola
PR -> DB  : query
DB --> PR : user data
PR --> AS : User
AS -> AS  : Verifica password (bcrypt)
AS --> AC : profilo studente
AC --> GW : profilo studente
GW --> FE : profilo studente

@enduml